Jetha has to leave for America in next three days. Bagha and Nattu Kaka celebrate this and ask Jetha to give them a party. Jetha orders Pizza and French fries for them. He calls Bapuji to tell the news but Nattu Kaka stops him from doing so. Jetha thinks he had such a good day just because of Babita Ji as she told him have a nice day.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Sweden Sex Tournament: Declares Sex as a Sport | First European Sex Championship | Indian Society
snippet.description:
Explore the unconventional decision by Sweden to declare sex as a sport and organize the first-ever European Sex Championship in this thought-provoking video for the UPSC GS1 Indian Society exam. Understand the rationale behind Sweden's unique approach and its implications for societal norms and perceptions of sexuality. Analyze the potential impact on gender equality, sexual empowerment, and the broader discourse on sexual rights. Delve into the debates surrounding the classification of sex as a sport and the controversies associated with such events. Gain insights into the cultural and legal aspects of sexuality in the context of Indian society. Stay informed about the evolving perspectives on sexuality for the UPSC GS1 examination. Watch this video and expand your understanding of the complex dynamics between sex, sports, and societal norms.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 09 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 5th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay‚Äôs advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.description:
Sambhavna Seth‚Äôs full name is Sambhavna Surender Kumar Seth. We must have seen her on YouTube, in Big Boss, and in many bhojpuri songs. She had a lot of love for dance since childhood. From the very beginning, she wanted to become a heroine. To make a career, she went to Mumbai with her father and gave many auditions, but did not get work and came back to Delhi. She did not do any work for 1 year, then after gaining some confidence, she again came to Mumbai. Got a film after a lot of struggle. She has worked in songs of many big films but those songs did not become hits but everyone was quite impressed with her dance.
Then he got a chance to work in Bhojpuri songs. The first song became so famous that now she started getting a lot of work in the Bhojpuri industry. Time passed and she also appeared in many reality shows like Big Boss, Khatron ke khiladi and Desi Girl. Today she runs a YouTube channel named Sambhavna Seth Entertainment on which she posts vlogs.

snippet.description:
Heyy Deyyss ‚ù§Ô∏è

Uncovering the Secrets of Karen Long Neck Village |‡Æµ‡Æø‡Æö‡Æø‡Æ§‡Øç‡Æ§‡Æø‡Æ∞ ‡Æï‡Æø‡Æ∞‡Ææ‡ÆÆ ‡ÆÆ‡Æï‡Øç‡Æï‡Æ≥‡Øç üò± ‡Æá‡Æµ‡Øç‡Æ≥‡Øã ‡Æ™‡ØÜ‡Æ∞‡Æø‡ÆØ ‡Æï‡Æ¥‡ØÅ‡Æ§‡Øç‡Æ§‡Ææ ü§Ø ‚Äã 

We had an extraordinary encounter that left us in awe. We had the chance to witness an incredible experimental creation in the world of entertainment: a combination of a lion and a tiger known as the LIGAR. This magnificent breed is eight times larger than a typical lion or tiger, but despite its immense size, it had a surprising nature, almost like a giant toy.

here are some additional facts about ligers:
- Ligers are the largest known cat species in the world, even larger than their parents, the lion, and the tiger.
- Ligers have a unique appearance, with stripes from the tiger and a mane from the lion.
- Ligers are usually sterile and cannot reproduce, although there have been a few rare cases of ligers being able to mate with other ligers or with lions or tigers.
- Ligers are not found in the wild, as lions and tigers do not share the same habitats in the wild.
- Ligers are often bred in captivity, and there is some controversy surrounding the practice of breeding ligers and other hybrid animals.
- Ligers are known for their playful personalities and are often used in animal shows and attractions.
- Ligers have a lifespan of around 10-15 years, which is shorter than the lifespan of lions and tigers in the

But our adventure didn't stop there! We ventured into a village with a fascinating tradition that caught our attention. In Karen Gong Neck Village, we encountered a community of people known for their unique practice of elongating their necks. These polite and welcoming individuals sustain their livelihood by crafting and selling handmade items. To achieve elongated necks, they gradually add neck rings every four years, resulting in a truly remarkable sight.

here are some interesting facts about Karen Gong Neck Village:

- The Karen Long Neck tribe is originally from Myanmar (Burma) and migrated to Thailand in the 1980s.
- The women of the tribe wear brass rings around their necks, starting at a young age, which give the appearance of elongated necks. Contrary to popular belief, the rings do not actually lengthen the neck but rather push down the collarbone and ribcage to create the illusion of a longer neck.
- The Karen Long Neck tribe is just one of several hill tribes in northern Thailand, each with their own unique culture and traditions.
- The village is located in a mountainous region, surrounded by lush forests and rice paddies.
- Visitors to the village can learn about the tribe's traditional handicrafts, including weaving and embroidery, and purchase handmade souvenirs.
- The village is also home to a school, where children from the tribe can receive an education.
- The Karen Long Neck tribe has faced some controversy and criticism over the years, with some people arguing that the practice of wearing the neck rings is exploitative and objectifying. However, others argue that it is an important part of the tribe's cultural heritage and should be preserved.
- Despite the controversy, Karen Gong Neck Village remains a popular tourist destination, attracting visitors from all over the world who are interested in learning about the tribe's unique culture and traditions.

This captivating journey was filled with astonishing sights and remarkable cultural experiences.

Episode 3788: Pyarelal's Dilemma
--------------------------------------------------------
Pyaarelal gets into trouble as Sapna and Kalpana have accepted his proposal to get married. Earlier Sapna had not revealed her decision while Babita and Madhavi had asked Pyaarelal to accept Kalpana. As everyone discusses the matter at Popatlal's house, Dr. Hathi comes excited to his house. he announces that they have brought him another proposal for marriage. Anjali and Taarak discuss who will tell the truth to Sapna's family, he calls Sapna's mother but she thinks it to be a prank. Keep an eye out!

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of 'Bhide Bana Crorepati':
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSCH5ciwJoKjs1SCjN150tq

snippet.description:

Episode 24: Baalveer's Mother In Danger
-------------------------------------------------
Aageel abducts Bardol and takes him to Himbash Lok, and she tortures him to extract information about Shashvan Lok. Aageel learns about Baalveer and how he transformed him into Veer while staying with the Bharadwaj family. Kaashvi arranges a show slot for Veer at her friend's event. Kaashvi informs Veer that if he is able to satisfy the show's organizers, he may be rewarded handsomely. Veer and Eva execute a disappearing magic act, which surprises everyone.  Later, Veer's mother goes missing, as nobody knows her whereabouts.

Show Name ‚Äì Baalveer S3
Star Cast ‚Äì Dev Joshi, Aditi Sanwal, Ada Khan, Behzaad Khan, Aditya Ranvijay
Episodes No - 24, 4 June 2023
Produced By - Vipul D Shah

About the show: 
---------------------------
The new season of Baalveer follows the journey of the 24-year-old superhero who draws strength from his mother. In this season, Baalveer is stripped of his powers, magic, and memories and lives as a regular boy Veer. The season revolves around his journey from Veer to Baalveer, regaining his identity and the world he belongs to with the help of partner Kaashvi.
